{"tid":1862933,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[散播肺炎]SHK有位經理唔跟指引就返左工","createTime":"2020-02-05T01:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T08:01:38.000Z","uid":5674,"like":173,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"1cf5bdf05dd5c4e5263d5e58aef9b14dc6f774a7","tid":1862933,"uid":5674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:43:19.000Z","msg":"今次大鑊喇！<br />\n<br />\n聽講公司有位manager住深圳，但係星期一拖住個喼返左office。<br />\nOffice hour喺公司裡面走黎走去。<br />\nLunch嗰陣仲同同事同枱食飯 有講有笑咁。<br />\n<br />\n公司上星期已經出左指引話要求曾經前往內地嘅同事要自我隔離，而居住内地同事更要出示體溫紀錄表。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c25VyUc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc25VyUc.png&h=cfc61510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁嗰位星期一先落黎香港嘅manager 即係符合晒&rdquo;曾經前往內地&rdquo;同&rdquo;居住內地&rdquo;啦。點解佢仲未自我隔離？<br />\n點知佢喺大陸有無受感染架，隨時都係一個生化炸彈<br />\n佢咁樣上班即係無視公司防疫指引，將我哋全公司同事條命當係草<br />\n我而加好撚驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日搭lift嗰陣喺lift lobby仲見到佢<br />\n我即刻行慢兩步，寧願遲到都唔想同佢同lift呀！<br />\n<br />\n屌，咁計法....佢即係已經返左三日工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc99320953b3dcbaf4dcea5bf11992e2015a50e","tid":1862933,"uid":52897,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:45:03.000Z","msg":"無所謂啦，sell hk 係咁上下"},{"pid":"3526777aba4f2905160100f63650506e05cd0e51","tid":1862933,"uid":137248,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:46:15.000Z","msg":"上連登講又有用啦屌"},{"pid":"7f0f643c4f8047a42e644c580be822a83286f94b","tid":1862933,"uid":100398,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:48:25.000Z","msg":"喺新鴻基中心返工？"},{"pid":"a1a436169ab0ed6aa515a96bfd72a7f08e51352a","tid":1862933,"uid":5674,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"3526777aba4f2905160100f63650506e05cd0e51","tid":1862933,"uid":137248,"like":11,"dislike":0