內地&rdquo;同&rdquo;居住內地&rdquo;啦。點解佢仲未自我隔離？<br />\n點知佢喺大陸有無受感染架，隨時都係一個生化炸彈<br />\n佢咁樣上班即係無視公司防疫指引，將我哋全公司同事條命當係草<br />\n我而加好撚驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日搭lift嗰陣喺lift lobby仲見到佢<br />\n我即刻行慢兩步，寧願遲到都唔想同佢同lift呀！<br />\n<br />\n屌，咁計法....佢即係已經返左三日工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:02:12.000Z","msg":"周圍走播毒，好快會出現傳播"},{"pid":"bbedf0ce6766d2145632ce0ea4991e290981b5b9","tid":1862933,"uid":292479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:03:37.000Z","msg":"SHK HR後知後覺, 出個勁古怪email 比同事囉!!!!"},{"pid":"1804dead5d4489730af5e68e39f0440cee904bd8","tid":1862933,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:03:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"27c610ded5e51fa38f499af0e21b1cc9f44a1f9c","tid":1862933,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:03:59.000Z","msg":"希望佢會爆"},{"pid":"086bebb3d309c14eb49b7c813c33a6236ace07fe","tid":1862933,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbedf0ce6766d2145632ce0ea4991e290981b5b9","tid":1862933,"uid":292479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:03:37.000Z","msg":"SHK HR後知後覺, 出個勁古怪email 比同事囉!!!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:04:26.000Z","msg":"有無人開名"},{"pid":"eeed68c3300ccd1d08e6b91983c448d4eb21fc97","tid":1862933,"uid":292479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:05:48.000Z","msg":"開名啦, cap佢相同電話出嚟啦!!!"},{"pid":"5267e42bf584ce21d90d4cd7081a3f51a450ec41","tid":1862933,"uid":115337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T07:14:05.000Z","msg":"攬炒"},{"pid":"2a465b6fcf23bc6cc5e4098cf993c94fb59ec4ba","tid":1862933,"uid":105363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e3ee47d8617211de6c1ab06f75b69d2f91d6173